section.section:
Each fiscal year, in addition to the amounts required to be paid under paragraph (1) of this subsection, a participating governmental unit shall pay:
the special accrued liability contribution required by § 21-305.3 of this subtitle;
any withdrawal liability contribution required by § 21-305.5 of this subtitle;
an amount equal to 5% of the aggregate earnable compensation of its employees who are members of the Employees' Retirement System; and
any annual deficit payment required under § 21-305.4(c) of this subtitle.
